# Important Announcement

Vice has officially entered full-scale development.

From this point forward, the project will receive our full focus, dedication, and active development efforts. We are committed to pushing Vice forward with maximum momentum and delivering the features, improvements, and stability that the language deserves.

As part of this transition, all official information, documentation, news, development updates, downloads, and project resources are now available exclusively on our official website:

🌐 https://vice0lang.web.app

We would like to thank everyone who has supported Vice so far. Your feedback, bug reports, suggestions, and contributions continue to help shape the future of the language.

The journey is only beginning.

— Vice Team
